premise_source_doc_sentence: William McKinley Jr.  (  January 29 , 1843 -- September 14 , 1901  )  was an American politician and lawyer who served as the 25th President of the United States from March 4 , 1897 until his assassination in September 1901 , six months into his second term .
William McKinley  (  1843 -- 1901  )  , 25th President of the United States
